{"tid":2254093,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"我有情緒困擾......","createTime":"2020-10-22T14:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T09:59:44.000Z","uid":14609,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e4522fafc7c21006842d56cc21339d54bf89c87f","tid":2254093,"uid":14609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:37:45.000Z","msg":"如題，我同朋友想整一個app幫人同自己管理情緒。我一直都有情緒管理問題，之前用過mood tracking/ meditation (headspace)之類既apps，但係我覺得冇動力可以俾我繼續用落去，之後就冇再用啦，我好希望可以整到一個app出黎係令到大家都會想持續咁用落去，真係幫到人。<br />\n<br />\n另一個朋友就因為做嘢唔開心，曾經試過係夜晚打比輔導熱線，但發現十個有九個都唔聽，聽嗰個又好似唔係好識安撫/比意見，令到佢更加唔開心。<br />\n<br />\n仲有一個比較重要既原因，就係為手足提供一個安全既平台去抒發自己。每一次出黎翻到屋企都一定會聽到d閒言閒語，每一次睇新聞都會有種強大既無力感，我完完全全體會到有感而不能抒既感覺，真係只能夠大喊一場先可以感覺好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知道呢到都有好多人同我地一樣，可能因為種種原因而未能夠同人傾訴，所以我地好想幫大家，搵到一個安全既渠道去講野，抒發情緒。但至於點樣具體去做，去唔俾人偷data，我地仲傾緊。<br />\n<br />\n當務之急就係希望大家可以幫手填下份問卷，等我地知道大家有咩需求，我地可以點樣整呢個真係幫到人既app。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ea02faf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7</a><br />\n<br />\n我地都知道整個咁既app出黎會需要用到好多資源，需要大量專業意見、時間同金錢等等，所以都唔係話真係好樂觀，但係如果得到大家既支持，我地就一定會見步行步，努力整佢出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你地有咩意見都歡迎你地同我地講，有咩問題我地儘量答下，有興趣比下意見既人都可以係問卷入面留返名同電話，我地可以一齊交流下。<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ea02faf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ea02faf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FXnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7&d=LL0CSI02xgrrxVkOh%2Fu%2FRJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=ea02faf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/XnD6rXKjEgzyvRBz7</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該曬大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49aa5c3cb40b2cf530e533ec75215f30d7c0944","tid":2254093,"uid":14609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"用5分鐘就填得曬，可以唔留名，唔留電話，儘量share比手足填，我地最想幫佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44eeded126533a6140e9d9536fe3ea5847d6206","tid":2254093,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"其實坊間有社工、情緒輔導同防止自殺會之類既機構<br />\n<br />\n大家有情緒問題困擾可以搵佢哋"},{"pid":"d06f402d8f271134f3c174bc3c8b72a2cb08317d","tid":2254093,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44eeded126533a6140e9d9536fe3ea5847d6206","tid":2254093,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"其實坊間有社工、情緒輔導同防止自殺會之類既機構<br />\n<br />\n大家有情緒問題困擾可以搵佢哋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:41:54.000Z","msg":"不過如果有偏見既其實都係嗰句<br />\n此地無銀"},{"pid":"164eeaa2b8915fec23decef237b20f75fdb4ab44","tid":2254093,"uid":14609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d44eeded126533a6140e9d9536fe3ea5847d6206","tid":2254093,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:41:01.000Z","msg":"其實坊間有社工、情緒輔導同防止自殺會之類既機構<br />\n<br />\n大家有情緒問題困擾可以搵佢哋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T14:43:35.000Z","msg":"係呀，但係太晏既話真係reach唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我都唔敢同其他人傾"},{"pid":"551cd495ee00d3e516